Name: Field & Stream: Total Outdoorsman Challenge
Overview: Field & Stream Total Outdoorsman Challenge brings you the thrill ofthe hunt! Play as the ultimate hunter, using real-life hunting skills tobag “trophy” animals from beautiful destinations throughout NorthAmerica. Hunt with a variety of weapons such as high-caliber huntingrifles, handguns and crossbows as you stalk and shoot your quarry inthis true life hunting simulation game. Step into the wild as you nabprized trophy animals for points, earnings and bragging rights backat the lodge. True adventure awaits with Field & Stream TotalOutdoorsman Challenge.
